       Several of the Predacons snapped to attention and drew thier wepons on 
the new, and rather dashing, fembot standing in the doorway of the engin 
room. "An invader!" Inferno cried, making his way closer.
       Megatron, stepping out from the shadows shoved Inferno to the floor 
and stepped in front of Quasar, "Hello, and you must be Black Aracnia's and 
Quickstrike's offspring, correct? Im Megatron, youre Commander."

       Aracnia and Gremlin looked on the monitor of a large solitary 
computer. On it was the blueprints of the vessle. Taking her claw, Aracnia 
traced out a path they could take.
       "This corridor has only three internal autoguns, we can take those out 
in a snap. All we need to do is to get in...here." She said, resting her claw 
on a small room. 
       Gremlin leaned closer, and then it hit him, what she was thinking was 
a good idea, and a perfect wa to get the drop on the Rebels and most 
importantly to get Quickstrike.
